reviewText:
Got tired of waiting on Netflix for this video.
So I bought it.
Well worth my money spent.
If you're into Jeeps you'll love this video

The Jeep was and always will be an interesting and collectible piece of American History. This DVD is very informative and takes the viewer right back to the beginnings of this true American Wonder. Well recommended viewing for the Jeep collector, history buffs and anyone curious about the "roots" of America's own, four-wheel-drive, OD "battle buggy.'
